languages.text: "Я не привык{mf||ла} к подобным знакам внимания от отважных воинов Арбитес. Весьма приятно".
"I am not accustomed to receiving such attentions from brave Arbites warriors. It is quite a pleasure."

languages.text: « Je n'ai pas l'habitude de faire l'objet d'une telle sollicitude de la part des vaillants guerriers de l'Arbites. C'est un réel plaisir. »
languages.original_text: "I am not accustomed to receiving such attentions from brave Arbites warriors. It is quite a pleasure."

languages.text: 「勇敢な高等裁定局の戦士からこんなふうに気にかけてもらえるのは慣れていないんだ。でもとても光栄だ」
languages.original_text: "I am not accustomed to receiving such attentions from brave Arbites warriors. It is quite a pleasure."

traits.locale_text: 「勇敢な高等裁定局の戦士からこんなふうに気にかけてもらえるのは慣れていないんだ。でもとても光栄だ」

languages.text: «No estoy acostumbrad{mf|o|a} a recibir semejante atención por valientes guerreros del Arbites. Es un placer».
languages.original_text: "I am not accustomed to receiving such attentions from brave Arbites warriors. It is quite a pleasure."

traits.locale_text: «No estoy acostumbrad{mf|o|a} a recibir semejante atención por valientes guerreros del Arbites. Es un placer».

languages.text: “我从来没体验过法务部的勇士对我献殷勤，这种感觉真是令人心花怒放。”
languages.original_text: "I am not accustomed to receiving such attentions from brave Arbites warriors. It is quite a pleasure."

traits.locale_text: “我从来没体验过法务部的勇士对我献殷勤，这种感觉真是令人心花怒放。”

languages.text: "Yürekli Arbites savaşçılarından böyle özel muamele görmeye alışkın değilim. Çok hoşuma gidiyor doğrusu."
languages.original_text: "I am not accustomed to receiving such attentions from brave Arbites warriors. It is quite a pleasure."

traits.locale_text: "Yürekli Arbites savaşçılarından böyle özel muamele görmeye alışkın değilim. Çok hoşuma gidiyor."

languages.text: "Ich bin es nicht gewohnt, von mutigen Kriegern des Arbites eine solche Aufmerksamkeit zu erhalten. Das ist eine wahre Freude."
languages.original_text: "I am not accustomed to receiving such attentions from brave Arbites warriors. It is quite a pleasure."
